## 10 things remember while creating microservices 
	# https://medium.com/javarevisited/10-things-to-keep-in-mind-while-designing-and-developing-microservices-8336ac1b7387 
	Design your services around business capabilities, not technical capabilities
	Define the boundaries of your microservices
	Design for resiliency
	Use lightweight communication protocols
	Use asynchronous communication between services
	Ensure data consistency between services
	Implement security measures
	Ensure scalability and performance
	Implement monitoring and logging
	Plan for testing and deployment
	Choose the right technology stack

